text: Yuka Watanabe (born 26 August 1967) is a Japanese equestrian. She competed in two events at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Japan Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
